# INNTEK AI API AGENT — Database Schema Reference
# Mirror of: master_blueprint.prompt § 6. Database Schema
# Version: 3.3.0 | Sync: 2026-03-03

## ORM: Sequelize 6.37.x | Dialect: MySQL 8 | File: back/src/models/index.js

---

## Tables (14 models)

### Roles
```sql
id          UUID        PK, DEFAULT UUIDV4
nombre      VARCHAR     UNIQUE, NOT NULL
createdAt   DATETIME    auto
updatedAt   DATETIME    auto
```

### Privilegios
```sql
id          UUID        PK, DEFAULT UUIDV4
ref_modulo  VARCHAR     NOT NULL  -- '*' = wildcard (all modules)
read        BOOLEAN     DEFAULT FALSE
write       BOOLEAN     DEFAULT FALSE
exec        BOOLEAN     DEFAULT FALSE
role_id     UUID        FK → Roles.id
createdAt   DATETIME    auto
updatedAt   DATETIME    auto
```

### Users
```sql
id          UUID        PK, DEFAULT UUIDV4
nombre      VARCHAR     NOT NULL
email       VARCHAR     UNIQUE, NOT NULL
password    VARCHAR     NOT NULL  -- bcrypt hash
role_id     UUID        FK → Roles.id
createdAt   DATETIME    auto
updatedAt   DATETIME    auto
```

### Tools
```sql
id                UUID        PK, DEFAULT UUIDV4
nombre            VARCHAR     NOT NULL
descripcion       TEXT
logo_herramienta  VARCHAR               -- emoji icon
training_prompt   TEXT                   -- System Instruction: Context
behavior_prompt   TEXT                   -- System Instruction: Behavior
response_format   VARCHAR               -- 'JSON' | 'Text' | 'Markdown'
output_format_id  UUID        FK → OutputFormats.id  (NULLABLE)
json_schema_id    UUID        FK → JsonSchemas.id    (NULLABLE)
ai_provider_id    UUID        FK → AiProviders.id    (NULLABLE, per-tool override)
createdAt         DATETIME    auto
updatedAt         DATETIME    auto
```

### JsonSchemas
```sql
id          UUID        PK, DEFAULT UUIDV4
nombre      VARCHAR     NOT NULL
descripcion TEXT
schema      TEXT        NOT NULL  -- JSON Schema as string
createdAt   DATETIME    auto
updatedAt   DATETIME    auto
```

### OutputCategories
```sql
id          UUID        PK, DEFAULT UUIDV4
nombre      VARCHAR     UNIQUE, NOT NULL
createdAt   DATETIME    auto
updatedAt   DATETIME    auto
```

### OutputFormats
```sql
id          UUID        PK, DEFAULT UUIDV4
nombre      VARCHAR     NOT NULL
tipo        ENUM('reporte','accionable','generativo')  DEFAULT 'reporte'
estructura  TEXT        NOT NULL  -- HTML template with {{placeholder}}
category_id UUID        FK → OutputCategories.id
createdAt   DATETIME    auto
updatedAt   DATETIME    auto
```

### Configs
```sql
id          UUID        PK, DEFAULT UUIDV4
key         VARCHAR     UNIQUE, NOT NULL
value       TEXT
createdAt   DATETIME    auto
updatedAt   DATETIME    auto
```

### AiProviders
```sql
id              UUID        PK, DEFAULT UUIDV4
nombre          VARCHAR     NOT NULL
slug            VARCHAR     UNIQUE, NOT NULL
tipo            ENUM('google_native','openai_compatible')  NOT NULL
api_key         VARCHAR               -- masked on GET (last 4 chars only)
base_url        VARCHAR               -- null for google_native
modelo          VARCHAR     NOT NULL
is_default      BOOLEAN     DEFAULT FALSE
activo          BOOLEAN     DEFAULT TRUE
extra_headers   TEXT                   -- JSON string for custom HTTP headers
createdAt       DATETIME    auto
updatedAt       DATETIME    auto
```

### Engines
```sql
id              UUID        PK, DEFAULT UUIDV4
nombre          VARCHAR     NOT NULL
slug            VARCHAR     UNIQUE, NOT NULL
descripcion     TEXT
tipo            ENUM('iterator','collector','mapper')  NOT NULL
icono           VARCHAR               -- emoji icon
config_schema   TEXT                   -- JSON string defining config fields
activo          BOOLEAN     DEFAULT TRUE
createdAt       DATETIME    auto
updatedAt       DATETIME    auto
```

### Machines
```sql
id          UUID        PK, DEFAULT UUIDV4
nombre      VARCHAR     NOT NULL
descripcion TEXT
icono       VARCHAR               -- emoji icon
activo      BOOLEAN     DEFAULT TRUE
createdAt   DATETIME    auto
updatedAt   DATETIME    auto
```

### MachineNodes
```sql
id          UUID        PK, DEFAULT UUIDV4
machine_id  UUID        FK → Machines.id  (ON DELETE CASCADE)
node_type   ENUM('tool','engine')  NOT NULL
tool_id     UUID        FK → Tools.id     (NULLABLE)
engine_id   UUID        FK → Engines.id   (NULLABLE)
position_x  FLOAT       DEFAULT 0
position_y  FLOAT       DEFAULT 0
config      TEXT                   -- JSON string for node-specific config
createdAt   DATETIME    auto
updatedAt   DATETIME    auto
```

### MachineConnections
```sql
id              UUID        PK, DEFAULT UUIDV4
machine_id      UUID        FK → Machines.id      (ON DELETE CASCADE)
source_node_id  UUID        FK → MachineNodes.id   (alias: SourceNode)
target_node_id  UUID        FK → MachineNodes.id   (alias: TargetNode)
source_handle   VARCHAR
target_handle   VARCHAR
createdAt       DATETIME    auto
updatedAt       DATETIME    auto
```

---

## Associations (models/index.js)

```
Role        1 ──────── N  Privilegio      (role_id)
Role        1 ──────── N  User            (role_id)
OutputCategory 1 ───── N  OutputFormat     (category_id)
OutputFormat   1 ───── N  Tool            (output_format_id)
JsonSchema     1 ───── N  Tool            (json_schema_id)
AiProvider     1 ───── N  Tool            (ai_provider_id)
Machine     1 ──────── N  MachineNode     (machine_id, CASCADE)
Machine     1 ──────── N  MachineConnection (machine_id, CASCADE)
MachineNode N ──────── 1  Tool            (tool_id)
MachineNode N ──────── 1  Engine          (engine_id)
MachineConnection N ── 1  MachineNode     as SourceNode (source_node_id)
MachineConnection N ── 1  MachineNode     as TargetNode (target_node_id)
```

---

### Roles: SuperAdmin, Admin, User
### Users: inntek (SuperAdmin role)
### Privilege Modules: Auth, AI_Tool_Maker, AI_Tool_Catalog, AI_Tool_Execution, Config, Outputs_Maker, Json_Schemas, AI_Providers, Machines
### AiProviders: Google Gemini (google_native), OpenRouter (openai_compatible, DEFAULT)
### Engines: list-iterator, list-collector, data-mapper
### OutputCategories: Identidad y Documentación, Reportes Ejecutivos
### OutputFormats: Reporte Validacion Cedula Chilena, Reporte Check Liquidacion Chile
### JsonSchemas: Esquema de Identidad Avanzado V2, Reporte Check Liqui Chile, Schema Lista Genérica
### Tools (11): Validador de CI Chile, CSS EXTRACTOR, Check de Liquidaciones Chile, CSV Data Extractor, Fleet Inventory Analyzer, Document Compliance Checker, Extractor de Nómina, Validador de Liquidación Individual, Verificador de Contrato, Verificador de Certificaciones, Generador de Reporte de Lote
### Machines (2): Verificación Laboral en Lotes (5 nodes, 4 connections), Verificación Documental Completa (8 nodes, 8 connections)

